<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.5">
<l>kaṭiyaṉ koṭiyaṉ neṭiya mālula kaṅkoṇṭa</l>
<l>vaṭiya ṉaṟivaru mēṉi māyatta ṉākiluṅ</l>
<l>koṭiyaveṉ ṉeñca mavaṉeṉṟē kiṭakku mellē,</l>
<l>tuṭiko ḷiṭaimaṭat tōḻī yaṉṉaiyeṉ ceyyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if he is harsh, cruel, tall Māl, he whose foot</l>
<l>took the world, marvellous one with a body rare in knowledge,</l>
<l>my cruel heart [still] keeps saying “he”, oh,</l>
<l>[my] innocent friend with hour-glass waist. What will mother do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
